[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "久しぶりに戻ってきたよ、オーベンランド",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00365",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "話には聞いていたけど、静かで寂しい雰囲気の場所だね\n",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00366",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "そうだね、世界の果てと言われても\n納得できるような所さ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00367",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "この先に広がる、暗く、寂しく、荒涼とした氷の海――\nそこには強力な魔物がたくさんいる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00368",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "暗黒の氷海、でしょ。\n大丈夫、覚悟は決めてきたよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00369",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "この先は、「九偉人図」の情報を基に進むんだよね。\n前回はなかったけれど、今回はこの手掛かりがある",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00370",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "ああ。「九偉人図」には、果ての大陸への道筋が\n星の位置や方角で示されている。危険が少ない道筋がね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00371",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "危険がまったくないわけじゃないが、私たちは今確かに\nこれまでで最も果ての大陸へ近づいている……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00372",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "兄さんの夢が叶いそうで、私も嬉しいよ。\n王国の未来的にもね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00373",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "クレオ……兄想いのよくできた妹よ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00374",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "小さい頃はね、兄さんのこと私が守って\n面倒見てあげなきゃって思ってたんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00375",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "あっちにふらふら、こっちにふらふらしてたからね。\nあ、それは今も同じか！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00376",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "甲斐性なしで悪かったね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00377",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "まあでも、今の兄さんならきっと私は必要ない。\nそう思ったんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00378",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "クレオ……そんなことはない、\n兄さんには妹が必要だとも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00379",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "いや、ブラッドさんがいるから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00380",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "さっきから上げては落としてくるね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00381",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "ゴホン！　にしても……多分この光景、\nオルペウス兄上も見たかったと思うんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00382",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "そうなの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00383",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "理由は違うけどね。私は冒険、兄上は実利。\n果ての大陸に眠るマナがあれば国民は豊かになる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00384",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "オルペウス兄さん……長男だから、きっと色々\n我慢して、頑張ってくれてるんだよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00385",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "そうだね、私やクレオのわがままを許して、\nランターナもしっかりまとめてくれてる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00386",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "すごい人だよ。さっきのクレオじゃないけど、\n私も兄上を支えてあげたい。不甲斐ない弟だけどね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00387",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "私も！　よくできた妹としてオルペウス兄さんの\n力になってあげるんだ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00388",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ほう、兄弟のいる国家は跡目争いで揉めがちだが、\nランターナは兄弟仲も良好のようだな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_038_00389",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "もしかして、向こうの会話が聞こえるんですか？\n耳聡いですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00390",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "私だってこの距離くらいならなんとか……！\nユリウス探しで鍛えた目と耳で！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00391",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "お母さんは張り合わないで、ね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00392",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "絶対的な王が君臨する国は繁栄する。\nランターナ王国は安泰かもしれんな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_038_00393",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "うん、私たちの国は大丈夫だなって思う。\n王族がこんなに近くて、優しいなんて！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00394",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "私も色々よくしてもらってるし……\n今回の旅で受けた恩、少しでも返せるといいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00395",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]